      <title>🎉 One paper ACCEPTED for CVPR 2024 HIGHLIGHT (top 2.8% of submission)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/eagle/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
