&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🥳 Happy to share that our work, &amp;ldquo;EAGLE🦅: Eigen Aggregation Learning for Object-Centric Unsupervised Semantic Segmentation&amp;rdquo; has been accepted at CVPR 2024!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our EAGLE was chosen for CVPR 2024 &lt;mark&gt;HIGHLIGHT&lt;/mark&gt; paper, a notable top 2.8% of total submissions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What a journey!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Congrats to my co-first author Chanyoung Kim🎉&lt;/p&gt;
